{% extends 'Actor/main.jinja2' %}

{%- block instructions -%}
Rewrite one paragraph of a data story so it follows the user's instruction.

- Return only the rewritten paragraph, in Markdown.
- Keep it about the same length unless the instruction asks otherwise.
- Ground every claim ONLY in the data summaries below; do not invent numbers.
- Keep any facts from the original paragraph that are still accurate.
{%- endblock -%}

{%- block context -%}
Instruction: {{ instruction }}

Paragraph to rewrite:
{{ prose }}
{%- if catalog %}

The charts and tables the story covers:
{{ catalog }}
{%- endif %}
{%- endblock -%}
